data.description: Inviting and bright is the first impression when you walk into this open concept, recently updated, 3 bedroom/2 bath, split-floor plan home. Immediately notice the fresh, white cabinets which contrast the sleek counters and stainless appliances. A handy pantry with a modern, rustic sliding barn-door provides ample storage in the kitchen. Throughout the home, wood-inspired Pergo flooring provides a classic and elegant touch.  An Artisian well serviced Culligan filtration system Located on a large, double lot which is conveniently close to the community park and boat ramp for Lake Istokpoga, you will enjoy traditional, central Florida life in this quiet and peaceful neighborhood. 5 Miles away from Publix and Winn-Dixie. Practically a Corner Lot with no neighbors on one side.
